headline: Labcorp price target raised to $305 from $300 at Evercore ISI
summary: Evercore ISI raised the firm’s price target on Labcorp (LH) to $305 from $300 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares. The firm’s survey work points to a positive outlook for preclinical CROs, with rising budgets and declining cancellations, along with suggesting stable demand for discovery and toxicology services into 2025 and 2026, the analyst tells investors in a note on the group.
